'''GPM''' is an abbreviation used for output of [[water]] by tankless [[water heater]]. It is the "[[gallon]]s per [[minute]]" the heater can raise by a certain [[temperature]].
----
In [[computing]], GPM (General Purpose Mouse), a mouse server for the console and xterm, with sample clients included (emacs, etc). 

